import { Box } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const example = () => {
  return (
    <container maxWidth="sm">
<Box sx={{padding : 3 , borderRadius : 1 , boxShadow : 3}}>
    <Typography variant ="h4" gutterBottom>
        Update patient 
    </Typography>

</Box>
    </container>
  )
}

export default example
